"EuroMillions?"</em>, it generates a plausible answer based on general "
"knowledge — often inaccurate or outdated. When you ask the same "
"question to HYBRIDE, it queries the database in real time and gives "
"you the <strong>real answer</strong>, up to date with the latest draw."

